	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro datis ad me scriptis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Nicht erhalten.</note> gratiam tibi habeo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod literę meae<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Oben <ref target="file10920">Nr. 879</ref>.</note> tardius missae sunt, causam intellexisti ex ipsis, ni fallor.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tecum autem sentio illos optimos viros infęlices esse in explicando hoc negotio<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Offenbar hatte <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> Äußerungen <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucers</persName> und <persName ref="p5565" cert="high">Capitos</persName> zur Konkordienfrage kritisiert.</note>, id quod plus semel illis coram testatus sum, neque minim, cum in nullo alias negotio tam sint ardentes et frequentes et certe plus semel mea opera, utcumque exigua, usi sunt.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et videor ipse mihi <persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Lutheri</persName> mentem (ut sese nunc illa habet et quam testatur se nunquam non habuisse) probe intelligere.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam Lutherani omnes et totus Lutheranus populus illam<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> las irrtümlich</hi> ilium; <hi>s. unten <ref target="file10933">Nr. 891</ref>, 3-5.</hi></note> intelligeret!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid nuper ad vos scripserim, omnino excidit mihi argumento excepto, itaque descriptam epistolam abs te peto.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea vale et ora dominum pro me et toto isthoc negotio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiae</placeName>, 28. augusti 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus totus <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Io. Zvick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, fratri observando.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͦ Zurch.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
